Package nbt.tag

Class CompoundTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • nbt.tag.Tag
      • nbt.tag.CompoundTag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Tag>
    public class CompoundTag
extends Tag
implements java.lang.Iterable<Tag>
    A tag that contains an unspecified number of tags that are guaranteed to contain a name and a payload corresponding to the type of that tag. It follows the specification laid out by the ByteArrayTag in the NBT format.
    Author:
    Killerkoen
